{"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","lang":"english","lang_option":"2","device":"dotpad320","audioPath":"","items":[{"page":1,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"2.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"2.txt","data":"20200A0B00200A0020200D25071E0A0F073D0000202039002020033D003C1A321A090932323200002001000E0A191100270A113A003700203D250D0A0E0A1E1E2C00011E00010019110E0502003E00010E0F1111210003250607110001032700133B00001302193200000000000000000000000000000000","plain":"IF I MULTIPLY  THIS BY 0.033...\nA side view of Yumi sitting at a desk, with a speech bubble above her head."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":21,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"2.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"2.txt","data":"2020132513260020203A010A1E02000000000000202039011E04200E0020201D00202010173232322001000E0A191100270A113A003700203D250D0A0E0A1E1E2C00011E00010019110E0502003E00010E0F1111210003250607110001032700133B00001302193200000000000000000000000000000000","plain":"HUH? WAIT,\nTHAT'S NOT RIGHT...\nA side view of Yumi sitting at a desk, with a speech bubble above her head."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":20,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"5.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"5.txt","data":"","plain":"UGH...THIS IS SO HARD! \n\"SCRATCH\"\n\"SCRATCH\"\nYumi has a worried expression and is scratching her forehead with her index finger."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":19,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"7.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"7.txt","data":"202009150D11002020151D0020201B253D0E160020200F251E0020203D33170020200C17221B390020201E151B112E17160020140E0A191100000000203D250D0A040E000D14190200091107070E00001C1100190A070A1B221E073D000E0F141D2C00013A151519220017151E011E2C000F07011E113200","plain":"COME ON GUYS!\nPUT YOUR\nSTRENGTH\nTOGETHER!\nInside Yumi's mind, cells are diligently spinning a wooden rotating plate."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":18,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"8.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"8.txt","data":"202010113D1015002020103A0020201E1B17000020201E150020201E25171D0020202E000000000020200D0A07070C1015160020010D0A190C002E00091107070E001E001C110003250E3D00000000000E0F141D2C002E003A151519220017151E011E2C0F07011E110200101500091107070000000000000E25191922073D0029331E0E3200000000000000","plain":"EVERYONE WORK TOGETHER TO TURN THE MILLSTONE!\nAmidst the cells that are busy spinning the wooden rotating plate, one cell suddenly shouts."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":6,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"6.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"6.txt","data":"","plain":"- RATIONAL CELL -\nYOU GUYS ARE JUST A BIT STIFF SINCE YOU HAVEN'T DONE THIS IN A WHILE!\nThe rational cell is cupping its hands around its mouth and shouting loudly."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":16,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"12.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"12.txt","data":"","plain":"CREAK- CREAK-\nHOW LONG'S IT BEEN?? IT BEEN?? IT WON'T EVEN BUDGE!!\nThree hardworking cells are diligently turning a wooden wheel with creaking sounds."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":15,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"8.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"8.txt","data":"","plain":"ONE~ TWO!\n\"YEAH, IT'S BETTER FOR HER TO AT LEAST USE IT A LITTLE BIT A LITTLE BIT EACH DAY!\"\nOn the left, there's one cell calling out commands, and next to it are three cells turning the wooden spinning wheel.\n"},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":14,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"16.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"16.txt","data":"","plain":"\"COME ON! WE'VE GOTTA FINISH THIS CALCULATION TO GO HOME FROM WORK!\"\nThe Rational Cell on the left is pointing somewhere with its index finger."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":13,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"10.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"10.txt","data":"","plain":"- EMOTIONAL CELL -\nCOULD SOMEONE PLEASE SHUT HER UP?\n\"I DON'T WANT TO WORK OVERTIME! I JUST WANT TO RUN INTO THE SHIMMERING, RED SUNSET.\"\nThe Emotional Cell is speaking with a quivering voice, and next to it are three other cells."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":12,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"20.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"20.txt","data":"","plain":"- RAMPAGE CELL - \n\"WHO CARES ABOUT ALL THIS CALCULATING CRAP-I JUST WANNA BLOW EVERYTHING TO PIECES...\"\"CALM DOWN, RAMPAGE...\nThere is a side view of the Hysterius Cell, with one eye covered by an eyepatch. Next to it, another cell appears shocked by its angry expression."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":11,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"22.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"22.txt","data":"","plain":"-NAUGHTY CELL-\n\"HEY GUYS, THERE'S NO ONE ELSE IN THE OFFICE. ...SO WHY DON'T WE...\"\n\"PUT SOME PANTS ON! YOU LUNATIC!!\"\nThe Naughty Cell is speaking, and next to it, two cells looking flustered."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":10,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"23.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"23.txt","data":"202013113D00202010113D1015160020202E000020200D0A07070C10150020200C1C1E2B0000000020201E25171D2C16160020200F251E0020203D172020030109050E002020141E150020202D16160020010D0A190C002E00091107070E001E25171D2C2E003A15151922000E0F141D2C0031111107020010150009110707000A0E0029331E2C3200000000","plain":"HEY EVERYONE!\nTHE MILLSTONE STARTED TURNING!!\nPUT YOUR BACKS INTO IT!!\nAmidst the cells turning the wooden spinning wheel, one cell is shouting."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":9,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"14.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"14.txt","data":"20200E0E2420200E05002015273B002E00000000091107070E0017151E011E2C002E003A151519223111110702000100030A1B000B15151E0F17141E2901192A00010F0F111C0E003E002E001E112D1E182620200E0E2420200E05321834000000000000","plain":"SS-SK\nOver the cells rotating the wooden wheel, a big footprint shadow appears with the text \"SS-SK.\""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":8,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"15.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"15.txt","data":"20200E1F2501291600200100071C1B11000000000B15151E000C150D0F0E00151D002E0000000000091107070E0200010F0F111C2C003E002E0000000E281900182620200E1F25012932183400000000","plain":"SQUASH!\nA large foot stomps on the cells, appearing with the sound \"SQUASH.\""},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":7,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"16.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"16.txt","data":"","plain":".....\nWHAT’RE YOU DOING HERE?\nOn the left, a cell is looking up at the large foot in shock, and on the right, the face of the panicked cell is zoomed in for emphasis."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":6,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"27.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"27.txt","data":"","plain":"- HUNGER CELL - \"I WANNA EAT SOMETHING.\"\nA gigantic Hunger Cell is speaking, and next to it, a tiny cell is looking up at it."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":5,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"28.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"28.txt","data":"203D250D0A0013010E0001001B171E073D000000291509052B00112D0F17110E281D0200000000000112150D0F011D0A2B00033D001E3A1500000000112D0907010D01301D000D1C050E320000000000","plain":"Yumi has a greatly shocked expression, accompanied by two exclamation marks."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":4,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"19.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"19.txt","data":"20201D1532323200200A0020201A002020011E11202019141D3B0020201D00202007301B000000002020011B15323232002001000E0A191100000000270A113A003700203D250D0A000E0A1E1E2C0000011E00010019110E0502003E0001000E0F11112103250607110001032700133B0013021932000000","plain":"NO… I JUST ATE DINNER NOT LONG AGO…\nA side view of Yumi sitting at a desk, with a speech bubble above her head."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":3,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"20.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"20.txt","data":"20201A0020200511110F0000000000000000000020201B152C32323220200B1509250E323232000020151D002E0007110B1E000A0E0001000E0A1911270A113A003700203D250D0A000E0A1E1E2C0000011E00010019110E0502002F00151D002E0010170A0E00203D250D0A001B170119250107073D000007021D2C003F3A1C190015273B002D3200000000","plain":"JUST KEEP GOING…FOCUS...\nOn the left is a side view of Yumi sitting at a desk, and on the right is Yumi gradually leaning forward over it."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":2,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"32.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"32.txt","data":"20201D2A002020061B140E0020202E000000000020200C15173D002020370020203D250D0A00000020202F002020133B0020200317011400000000002020091107070E320020102E000A0E0001000000270A113A003700203D250D0A040E000301090500350029110017251D0E0014000100132517173D32","plain":"NOW BEGINS THE STORY OF YUMI AND HER BRAIN CELLS.\nThere is a view of Yumi's back as she runs in a hurry."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}},{"page":1,"title":"Ep. 0 - Prologue","graphic":{"name":"33.dtm","data":""},"text":{"name":"33.txt","data":"20151D002E0007110B1E0200102E000A0E000000203D250D0A040E000B01091102002F00151D002E101702000E10110107000E0D010707000911070710210E00090006000E1122003A0107052C000000141E1500203D250D0A040E000D14193200000000","plain":"On the left, there is Yumi's face, and on the right, several small cell characters can be seen walking into Yumi's mind."},"audio":{"fileName":"","tempFile":""}}]}